1. Download the latest pocketsphinx version (minimum 0.8)

2. Replace the original `src/programs/continuous.c` with the modified version `speech_recognition/fatpocketsphinx/modified_continuous.c`

3. Compile it and copy the `pocketsphinx_continuous` binary to `speech_recognition/fatpocketsphinx/fatpocketsphinx_continuous` (or create a symlink)


